file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 20-30-05-02 - PAINTING MATERIALS - MAINTENANCE PRACTICES

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL PAINTING MATERIALS - MAINTENANCE PRACTICES EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. This subchapter gives a list of the products approved to be used on, and for the servicing of, the aircraft, with their most usual suppliers. B. The correct procedure to use the products must be referred to in the chapters given in the table. C. Products with the same specification MIL-, FED. SPEC., but of different makes, must not be mixed. D. Possible alternative products are opposite the same group of chapters where the indicated product(s) is(are) referred to. E. Products given on the QPL (Qualified Products List) for specifications MIL referred to in this subchapter are automatically approved to be used on the aircraft. F. The supplier/manufacturer addresses are given in section AMM MPP 20-30-00/200. EMB-145 - AMM 1285 General 20-30-05 Page 1 of 5 Rev 55 - Oct 29/18 Copyright ÃÂ© by Embraer S.A.
